node.text:
You’re gonna go through some stuff. The key is to deal with the issues head on, love through it sometimes tough lessons some times easier lessons, bounce back and still love and take care of eachother. Family is a two way street. We are all learning how to love each other. Omere’s needs are different from Skylars who’s are different from Infinity and Aasim’s or Lil Mendeecees. Through trial and error we learn how to love each individual person and hope that child loves us back the way we need to be loved as a parent. #1 fact is as parents we want to love and help our children overcome emotional obstacles and embrace their worth in
order to reach their full potential. Strong, stable and secure kids  are not born, they’re raised! (My mission statement for EGL PUD is true in my house too) Tune In TONIGHT! 8pm on VH1 @loveandhiphop @vh1 
.
Here’s a little behind the scenes of what my house was like a few weeks after we shot the show. Families heal. Families grow. That’s all I pray for. Constant healing, understanding and growth♥️

With love,
Yandy

node.text:
Myself, @eglpuds along with Former Mayor Kasim Reed are joining forces to help with school supplies. I can not be in this community and not serve the community. I was able to connect with @kasimreed yesterday and  ask a lot of questions. We spoke at about POLICE BRUTALITY and his plan for the future, We spoke about GENTRIFICATION and the displacement of small black businesses, we spoke at length about Homelessness and the WEALTH EQUALITY GAP, AFFORDABLE HOUSING AND YOUTH EMPLOYMENT.  ALL of my concerns were his concerns and he actually had plans of action that would truly change what the ATLANTA community looks like. I don’t blindly support anyone so it was important for me to hear his point of view and plans. There is a link in my bio to help get him elected. Please click and support his campaign. 
.
@yelleskincare Store Give Away
55 Upper Alabama
Atlanta, GA 303030
1pm- Until supplies are gone.

node.text:
Myself along with @eglpuds and @kasimreed will be giving out @blendeddesigns back packs this Saturday starting at 1 until supplies run out. 

If you’re not in Atlanta please support this small, black owned, woman owned business. She almost lost her business due to covid and schools being shut down. They’re trying their best to hold on but it will all depend on how well they do during this back to school season. 

Every year the owner @iamcaseyrkelley donates thousands of back packs to my non profit @eglpuds. This year Instead of her donating, I purchased them because she needs the support. 

So y’all be sure that we spend all that back to school money in the right place and help @blendeddesigns stay  afloat. 

And if you are in A-town come see me this Saturday at the Yelle store. I’ll be giving out back packs to adults with children, while supplies last.

node.title: Back to School Give Away X @yelleskincare Store

Then turned around and took her new born baby for NO REASON AT ALL. This is not humane! If you go to @syesha’s page and look at the latest ill use of power over this BLACK WOMEN’s womb magic you would be appalled, disgusted, broken and confused! HOW CAN THIS HAPPEN?!!! There have been terrible reports even from the media about the doctor that caused the removal. One women committed suicide because she was not able to get her baby back. Please join me in reposting and help us fight for her babies to make it home NOW!! Queen Syesha and her KING. We are with you. We are fighting, praying and hurting for you. Let’s make this story trend. #bringRaHome #bringRAHhome

✨NOW AVAILABLE ✨ YELLE’s New Fresh Start preventative system is here! 
.
While you take advantage of our introductory 20% off sale with code FRESH , let’s dive into each product !
.
✨Fresh Start Mattify Mask : This fast-acting daily or weekly mask is for pimple-prone skin treats and repairs blemished skin while actively foiling future flare-ups.

✨Fresh Start Blemish Away Mask: Use our Fresh Start Blemish Away Mask as a spot treatment for day and night with blemish banishing willow bark extract. This synergistic blend of scientifically proven blemish battlers keeps troubled skin clean and clear. Non irritating like other spot treatments, topical application is the answer to blemished skin troubles.

✨ Fresh Start Milk & Honey Cleanser:Made with Coconut Milk, Natural Honey Gel, Infused with Papaya Enzymes, Apricot Kernel Oil & Vitamin E.

✨Fresh Start Daily Moisturizer : Pamper your skin and let all the goodness of this moisturizer sink in without leaving a greasy feeling. YELLE Organic Herbal Infusion® A Plant-Based daily moisturizer, the perfect companion to the complete regimen.

#yelleskincare
